WALLACE
v.
FT. MYERS PARTNERSHIP, et al. No. 257P08-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 26, 2008. Coward Law Firm, Washington, DC, for Ft. Myers Partnership, et al.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 21st day of July 2008 by Plaintiff to Supplement Petition to Vacate:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference this the 26th day of August 2008."
